# Ecommerce Standards

Pricing should feel premium.

Avoid:

- giant discount badges
- flashy offers
- red sale labels

## Cart

Use slide-out drawer.

Never redirect user.

Use AnimatePresence.

## Product Pages

Focus on:

- Storytelling
- Craftsmanship
- Materials
- Details

Not aggressive selling.
